      text1: "Tooth pain or infection can be overwhelming—especially while traveling. Our clinic provides professional root canal treatment for American patients seeking fast, safe, and effective dental care in Mexico.",
      text2: "If you are searching for a root canal near me while visiting Playa del Carmen, our team is prepared to diagnose and relieve pain as quickly as possible.",
      imageSrc: imgPath + "Root-canal-IMG-2.webp",
