      text1: "Root canal treatment, also known as endodontic treatment, removes infected or damaged tissue from inside the tooth. The goal is to eliminate pain, stop infection, and preserve the natural tooth.",
      text2: "This treatment allows patients to avoid tooth extraction while restoring comfort and oral health.",
    },
    indications: {
      title: "When Is a Root Canal Needed?",
