        "Persistent tooth pain",
        "Sensitivity to hot or cold",
        "Swelling or infection",
        "Pain when chewing",
        "A cracked or deeply decayed tooth"
      ],
      footerText: "An evaluation by a root canal dentist is essential to determine the correct treatment."
    },
    specialist: {
      title: "Root Canal Treatment by an Endodontist",
      text1: "Procedures are performed by a trained endodontist in Playa del Carmen. Working with a root canal specialist ensures precision, comfort, and long-term success.",
